OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FWarm sunny
OL,6,Fspells will give way to a risk of rain
OL,7,Fand showers for a time, edging
OL,8,Feastwards. These showers may be heavy
OL,9,Fand thundery. Becoming generally drier
OL,10,Flater in the night. Mostly mild, but
OL,11,Fchilly in western rural areas.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FMainly fine. Brightest early
OL,14,Fon, with some warm sunny spells and
OL,15,Flight winds, although cloud amounts
OL,16,Fgenerally increasing as the day
OL,17,Fprogresses. Likely staying dry until
OL,18,Fthe evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
